description.en:
What is SWISS ?
• SWISS is a farming protocol implementing liquidity and price arbitrages features in its own ecosystem thanks to new concepts such as Proof of Volume.

How does it work ?
• SWISS allows users to farm while the protocol arbitrates in price and liquidity for the ecosystem to grow making it not only a deflationary farming platform but also delivering an exponential growth to the ecosystem.

What is the added value for users ?
• Each time a user buys or sells SWISS, 3% is withdrawn in the form of SWISS and put back into two wallets (2% and 1%) that arbitrages automatically thanks to a code.
